import { Icon } from '@iconify/react'; import { pageTitle } from '../../../helper'; import Div from '../../Div'; import Spacing from '../../Spacing'; import React ,{useState , useContext , useEffect} from 'react' import axios from 'axios' import {useParams} from 'react-router-dom' const initialeState ={ username:'', email:'', password:'', role:'', _id : '' } function UpdateUser() { const HandleChangeInput = e =>{ const {name , value} = e.target setOffer({...offer , [name]:value}) } const HandleSubmit = async e =>{ e.preventDefault() try { if(!isAdmin) return alert("vous n'étes pas un admin.") if(!images) return ('no image Upload.') if(onEdit){ await axios.put(`/user/updateUser//${user._id}` , {...offer ,img:images} , {headers :{Authorization :token}} )} else{ await axios.post('/api/offer' , {...offer ,img:images} , {headers :{Authorization :token}}) } setCallback(!callback) } catch (error) { alert(error.response.data.msg) } } const [User , setUser] = useState(initialeState) return ( <>
{onEdit ? :''}
) } export default UpdateUser
